snippet.title: Jump into Action with Magikarp Jump!
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/2qY6dl8
Train your Magikarp to soar as high as possible in Magikarp Jump! Magikarp now gets its time in the spotlight with this fun app for iPhone, iPad, and Android devices. Feed and develop your Magikarp to maximize its jump power to reach new heights! Can your Magikarp become League Champion?

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com 
Shop: http://www.pokemoncenter.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Pokemon 
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon 
Tumblr: http://www.pokemon.tumblr.com
